               I am sorry, that the years transactions of our scientific Societies are not yet fully printed, but I have given orders that a copy of the philos. transact. shall be transmitted to you, and will send reprints of the bot. articles of the Victorian Institute;

See B55.13.05, B55.13.06, B55.13.07.
                both societies are now united under the name Philosophical Institute, and promise to work well.
